snippet.textDisplay: Uff Nabeel Shaukat Ali! This re-worked Coke Studio version has taken this already beautiful song to another level. I loved watching Nabeel savour the lines and just enjoy the performance. The poetry is exquisite. And that gorgeous flute interlude! Take a bow Strings, all the musicians and everyone involved in creating this. It's going to be a highlight for Coke Studio 8 and we've only just started! No other words to describe this but beautiful. Will be listening to this over and over...
